cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with the deployment of deep learning models on smartphones, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) domains. The use of multi-threading and benchmarking also suggests the possibility of considering multimedia (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of neural networks for real-time inference can also be categorized under neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
